Subject: drm/i915: add io_size plumbing
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 235582ca96214b50fa03ea77a5e85e59d94cf358
